<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Karki</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-24 16:43:47</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Sorry folks but the Ring was removed from the game and is no longer received via the Thex Mallet quest. The ring was deemed too powerful for melee types and was removed. Anyone who acquired the ring before then still has it and they can be re-charged still. The rings where changed to No-Drop as well so if you don't have one now you will never get one. The Thex Mallet quest now only returns the Repear of the Dead weapon.<BR>
<BR>
BTW: Don't respond to this saying that there must still be someway to acquire this and if you just look for it hard enough you'll find. Trust me, this went the way of the Manastone and you'll never see it unless you already have it.</font></td></tr></table>
